{"type":"question","id":20357,"title":"如何看待美国CDC曾不公布新冠肺炎检测人数转而用Yes/no来代替本州是否有新冠感染者？","uid":2719,"topics":[1284,28,163,5262,4119],"contents":"<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/lhLwwF2.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lhLwwF2.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/lhLwwF2.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>https://i.guancha. cn/news/social/2020/03/04/20200304154530379.png<br>\n<br>\n第二张图找不到原出处，据观察者网说是来自《纽约时报》，但我没有找到相关文章，只能先用他们的图了。<br>\n现在CDC官网是显示人数的，不知道是不是因为Yes/No 引起很多人不满。<br>\n本来墙内的大家是对中共在疫情中隐瞒数据不满，结果美国CDC一通骚操作甚至连数据都懒得给，瞬间把国内舆论扭转方向，比烂党占领高地，反思体制派被重新压制讽刺。这会让多少摇摆不定的潜在反贼被重新打回去啊，明明疫情这么好的开民智反思的机会。我都要怀疑它们是不是被中共渗透完了。<br>\n<br>\n以下是知乎高赞：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/D1DXE7y.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/D1DXE7y.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/D1DXE7y.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/6gS8BIz.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6gS8BIz.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/6gS8BIz.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JGDZeKZ.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JGDZeKZ.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/JGDZeKZ.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/W1vpp9C.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W1vpp9C.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/W1vpp9C.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/5VxVIb6.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5VxVIb6.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/5VxVIb6.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/F4hjCXT.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/F4hjCXT.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/F4hjCXT.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/L4r